
Please use this rpm rocks-command-kvm-6.2-3.x86_64.rpm
to replace one that came with KVM roll for Rocks 6.2

Installation instructions:

cp rocks-command-kvm-6.2-3.x86_64.rpm  /export/rocks/install/contrib/
(cd /export/rocks/install/; rocks create distro)
yum list rocks-command-kvm
yum update rocks-command-kvm
rocks run host vm-container "yum update rocks-command-kvm"

